fr.istic.m2il.aoc.observerasynchrone.channel

Class Channel

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.istic.m2il.aoc.observerasynchrone.channel.Channel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GeneratorAsync, ObserverAsync<Generator>, Subject<GeneratorAsync>

    public class Channel
extends java.lang.Object
implements ObserverAsync<Generator>, GeneratorAsync, Subject<GeneratorAsync>
    Represents the proxy in Active Object Pattern. Its plays proxy role twice, on one side from Subject of GeneratorAsync to ObserverAsync of Generator as async generator and other side from ObserverAsync of Generator to Subject of GeneratorAsync
